<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Newton-Raphson Method - Question 2</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: url('img/mcsc.png') no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .results {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        form {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Newton-Raphson Method - Question 2</h1>
        
        <div class="results">
            <h3>Implement the Newton-Raphson method to approximate the root of the equation e^x -4x by taking the initial guess x0=1.0</h3>
            
            <h2>Iterations:</h2>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Iteration</th>
                    <th>x</th>
                    <th>f(x)</th>
                    <th>f'(x)</th>
                </tr>
                <% for (let i = 0; i < iterations.length; i++) { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= iterations[i].iteration %></td>
                        <td><%= iterations[i].x %></td>
                        <td><%= iterations[i].fx %></td>
                        <td><%= iterations[i].fprimeX %></td>
                    </tr>
                <% } %>
            </table>
            
            <% if (root !== null) { %>
                <h2>Root:</h2>
                <p>The estimated root is: <%= root.toFixed(4) %> </p>
            <% } else { %>
                <h2>Root:</h2>
                <p>No root found within the specified tolerance.</p>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <form action="/" method="get">
            <input type="submit" value="Back to Home" />
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
